TY  - JOUR
TI  - Conditional Expected Utility
AU  - Luce, R. Duncan
AU  - Krantz, David H.
AB  - [This paper describes empirical laws (formulated abstractly, as axioms) that lead to simultaneous measurement of utility and subjective probability under circumstances where decisions delimit which states of nature may occur.]
